# Technical SEO — mobile

Primary Google index profile. PSI/Lighthouse **Mobile**.

| Metric | Target | Tactics |
|--------|--------|---------|
| LCP | ≤2.5s | Mobile LCP = hero **H1 text** (no hero image below `md`); desktop-only preload with `media="(min-width: 768px)"`; `hero-item` opacity 1 on mobile |
| INP | ≤200ms | lazy `HeaderMobileMenu`; Turnstile on intersect; passive scroll; carousel edge sentinels (no `scrollWidth` reads) |
| CLS | ≤0.1 | image dimensions; reserved hero `min-h`; aspect-ratio on cards/articles |

Touch ≥44px (`TW_TOUCH`) · no horizontal scroll · manifest/viewport/theme_color · content parity with desktop.

## Image rules (PSI)

- Homepage hero: `lcpHeroImageProps()` in `sanity/lib/image.ts` — srcset + `LcpImagePreload` with `media="(min-width: 768px)"`
- Leaf heroes: `leafHeroImageUrl()` · `sizes="100vw"` on fill `Image`
- Article featured: `articleFeaturedImageUrl()` · `loading="lazy"` (below H1)
- Below-fold sections: `TW_CV_AUTO` on homepage blocks, footer, listing grids
- Carousel: sentinel `IntersectionObserver` for prev/next — never read `scrollWidth` / `scrollLeft`
- Reveal: no JS on mobile (`globals.css` shows `.rv-*`); avoids forced reflow on homepage

